Title: French terminal closures re-route some LNG ships, push back scheduled arrivals
Description: A four-day extension to a halt in operations at the Fluxys-operated 9.6 mtpa Dunkerque LNG receiving terminal in France due to strike action has led to a pushback in the scheduled arrival of one ship and a change in the path of another, while more ships have diverted away from the countryâ€™s three other shuttered LNG terminals.
Author: CK
